    <name>CoreGarage</name>
    <summary>A settings manager for all the CSuite apps</summary>
    
    <description>
        <p>
            A settings manager for all the CSuite apps. This app can be used to change look, behaviors and settings of all the CSuite apps available in the Flathub. This can also be used to archive all the settings, pins created by CorePins, activities by CSuite and restore it later.
        </p>
        <p>Please use this app to change CSuite app settings and report your reviews, bugs and feature request in our report section in the links section below.</p>
    </description>
    
